[section#func.wrap.ref.ctor
    [:en] Constructors and assignment operators
    [:zh_CN] 构造函数和赋值运算符
]

[%@lib@raw [`function_ref::[*is-invocable-using]][%function_ref::is-invocable-using]]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<class... T>
  static constexpr bool [[redoc("*>")]]is-invocable-using = [[redoc("[=seebelow]")]];
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para]
[:en] If [^noex] is [`true], [`[*is-invocable-using]<T...>] is equal to:
[:zh_CN] 若 [^noex] 为 [`true]，则 [`[*is-invocable-using]<T...>] 等于：
[codeblock]
is_nothrow_invocable_r_v<R, T..., ArgTypes...>
[codeblock:end]
[:en] Otherwise, [`[*is-invocable-using]<T...>] is equal to:
[:zh_CN] 否则，[`[*is-invocable-using]<T...>] 等于：
[codeblock]
is_invocable_r_v<R, T..., ArgTypes...>
[codeblock:end]
[div:end]

[%@lib@raw [`function_ref::[*is-convertible-from-specialization]][%function_ref::is-convertible-from-specialization]]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<class... T>
  static constexpr bool [[redoc("*>")]]is-convertible-from-specialization = [[redoc("[=seebelow]")]];
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para]
[:en] If [`F] denotes a specialization [`function_ref<R(Args...) [=cv cv2] noexcept([^noex2])>]
for some placeholders [=cv cv2] and [^noex2], [`[*is-convertible-from-specialization]<F>] is equal to:
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`F] 代表针对某组占位符 [=cv cv2] 和 [^noex2] 的特例
[`function_ref<R(Args...) [=cv cv2] noexcept([^noex2])>]，
则 [`[*is-convertible-from-specialization]<F>] 等于：
[codeblock]
is_convertible_v<R(&)(Args...) noexcept([[redoc("^>")]]noex2), R(&)(Args...) noexcept([[redoc("^>")]]noex)> &&
is_convertible_v<int [[redoc("[=cv]")]]&, int [[redoc("[=cv cv2]")]]&>
[codeblock:end]
[:en] Otherwise, [`[*is-convertible-from-specialization]<F>] is [`false].
[:zh_CN] 否则，[`[*is-convertible-from-specialization]<F>] 为 [`false]。
[div:end]

[%@lib@ctor function_ref]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<class F> function_ref(F* f) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:constraints]
[list]
[item]
[:en] [`is_function_v<F>] is [`true], and
[:zh_CN] [`is_function_v<F>] 为 [`true]，并且
[item]
[:en] [`[*is-invocable-using]<F>] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] [`[*is-invocable-using]<F>] 为 [`true]。
[list:end]

[para:expects]
[:en] [`f] is not a null pointer.
[:zh_CN] [`f] 不是空指针。

[para:effects]
[:en] Initializes [*bound-entity] with [`f], and [*thunk-ptr] with the address
of a function [`[^thunk]] such that [`[^thunk]([*bound-entity], [^call-args]...)]
is expression-equivalent ([#defns.expression.equivalent]) to
[`invoke_r<R>(f, [^call-args]...)].
[:zh_CN] 以 [`f] 初始化 [*bound-entity]，并以某个函数 [`[^thunk]] 的地址初始化
[*thunk-ptr]，使得 [`[^thunk]([*bound-entity], [^call-args]...)] 按表达式等价于
（[#defns.expression.equivalent]）[`invoke_r<R>(f, [^call-args]...)]。
[div:end]

[%@lib@ctor function_ref]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<class F> constexpr function_ref(F&& f) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para]
[:en] Let [`T] be [`remove_reference_t<F>].
[:zh_CN] 令 [`T] 为 [`remove_reference_t<F>]。

[para:constraints]
[list]
[item]
[:en] [`remove_cvref_t<F>] is not the same type as [`function_ref], and
[:zh_CN] [`remove_cvref_t<F>] 与 [`function_ref] 为不同类型，并且
[item]
[:en] [`is_member_pointer_v<T>] is [`false], and
[:zh_CN] [`is_member_pointer_v<T>] 为 [`false]，并且
[item]
[:en] [`[*is-invocable-using]<[=cv] T&>] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] [`[*is-invocable-using]<[=cv] T&>] 为 [`true]。
[list:end]

[para:effects]
[:en] If [`[*is-convertible-from-specialization]<remove_cv_t<T>>] is [`false],
initializes [*bound-entity] with [`addressof(f)], and [*thunk-ptr] with
the address of a function [`[^thunk]] such that
[`[^thunk]([*bound-entity], [^call-args]...)] is expression-equivalent
([#defns.expression.equivalent]) to [`invoke_r<R>(static_cast<[=cv] T&>(f), [^call-args]...)].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`[*is-convertible-from-specialization]<remove_cv_t<T>>] 为 [`false]，
则以 [`addressof(f)] 初始化 [*bound-entity]，并以某个函数 [`[^thunk]] 的地址初始化
[*thunk-ptr]，使得 [`[^thunk]([*bound-entity], [^call-args]...)] 按表达式等价于（[#defns.expression.equivalent]）
[`invoke_r<R>(static_cast<[=cv] T&>(f), [^call-args]...)]。

[:en] Otherwise, initializes [*bound-entity] with the value of [`f.[*bound-entity]]
and [*thunk-ptr] with the value of [`f.[*thunk.ptr]].
[:zh_CN] 否则，以 [`f.[*bound-entity]] 的值初始化 [*bound-entity]，
并以 [`f.[*thunk.ptr]] 的值初始化 [*thunk-ptr]。

[para:remarks]
[:en] If [`remove_cvref_t<F>] is a specialization of [`function_ref],
an implementation may initialize [*bound-entity] with the value of
[`f.[*bound-entity]] and [*thunk-ptr] with the value of [`f.[*thunk-ptr]].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`remove_cvref_t<F>] 是 [`function_ref] 的特例，实现可能以
[`f.[*bound-entity]] 的值初始化 [*bound-entity]， 并以 [`f.[*thunk.ptr]] 的值初始化 [*thunk-ptr]。

[begin:example]
[codeblock]
void f1(std::string);
void f2(std::string);

function_ref<void(std::string)> r1(&f1);
function_ref<void(std::string&&)> r2(r1);
r2("");                 // [:en] [`f1] is invoked [:zh_CN] 调用 [`f1]
r1 = &f2;
r2("");                 // [:en] it is unspecified if [`f1] or [`f2] is invoked [:zh_CN] 未指明调用 [`f1] 还是 [`f2]
[codeblock:end]
[end:example]
[div:end]

[%@lib@ctor function_ref]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<auto c, class F> constexpr function_ref(constant_wrapper<c, F> f) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:constraints]
[:en] [`[*is-invocable-using]<const F&>] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] [`[*is-invocable-using]<const F&>] 为 [`true]。

[para:mandates]
[list]
[item]
[:en] If [`is_pointer_v<F> || is_member_pointer_v<F>] is [`true],
then [`f.value != nullptr] is [`true], and
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`is_pointer_v<F> || is_member_pointer_v<F>] 为 [`true]，则
[`f.value != nullptr] 为 [`true]，并且
[item]
[:en] if [`ArgTypes] is not an empty pack and all types in [`remove_cvref_t<ArgTypes>...]
satisfy [*:c constexpr-param] then
[`constant_wrapper<[^INVOKE](f.value, remove_cvref_t<ArgTypes>::value...)>] is not a valid type.
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`ArgTypes] 不是空包组且 [`remove_cvref_t<ArgTypes>...] 中的所有类型
均满足 [*:c constexpr-param]，则
[`constant_wrapper<[^INVOKE](f.value, remove_cvref_t<ArgTypes>::value...)>] 不是有效类型。
[list:end]

[para:effects]
[:en] Initializes [*bound-entity] with a pointer to an unspecified object or
null pointer value, and [*thunk-ptr] with the address of a function [`[^thunk]]
such that [`[^thunk]([*bound-entity], [^call-args]...)] is expression-equivalent
([#defns.expression.equivalent]) to [`invoke_r<R>(f.value, [^call-args]...)].
[:zh_CN] 以指向某个未指明对象的指针或空指针值初始化 [*bound-entity]，并以某个
函数 [`[^thunk]] 的地址初始化 [*thunk-ptr]，使得
[`[^thunk]([*bound-entity], [^call-args]...)] 按表达式等价于
（[#defns.expression.equivalent]）[`invoke_r<R>(f.value, [^call-args]...)]。
[div:end]

[%@lib@ctor function_ref]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<auto c, class F, class U>
  constexpr function_ref(constant_wrapper<c, F> f, U&& obj) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para]
[:en] Let [`T] be [`remove_reference_t<U>].
[:zh_CN] 令 [`T] 为 [`remove_reference_t<T>]。

[para:constraints]
[list]
[item]
[:en] [`is_rvalue_reference_v<U&&>] is [`false], and
[:zh_CN] [`is_rvalue_reference_v<U&&>] 为 [`false]，并且
[item]
[:en] [`[*is-invocable-using]<const F&, [=cv] T&>] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] [`[*is-invocable-using]<const F&, [=cv] T&>] 为 [`true]。
[list:end]

[para:mandates]
[:en] If [`is_pointer_v<F> || is_member_pointer_v<F>] is [`true],
then [`f.value != nullptr] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`is_pointer_v<F> || is_member_pointer_v<F>] 为 [`true]，则
[`f.value != nullptr] 为 [`true]。

[para:effects]
[:en] Initializes [*bound-entity] with [`addressof(obj)], and [*thunk-ptr] with
the address of a function [`[^thunk]] such that
[`[^thunk]([*bound-entity], [^call-args]...)] is expression-equivalent
([#defns.expression.equivalent]) to
[`invoke_r<R>(f.value, static_cast<[=cv] T&>(obj), [^call-args]...)].
[:zh_CN] 以 [`addressof(obj)] 初始化 [*bound-entity]，并以某个函数 [`[^thunk]]
的地址初始化 [*thunk-ptr]，使得 [`[^thunk]([*bound-entity], [^call-args]...)]
按表达式等价于（[#defns.expression.equivalent]）
[`invoke_r<R>(f.value, static_cast<[=cv] T&>(obj), [^call-args]...)]。
[div:end]

[%@lib@ctor function_ref]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<auto c, class F, class T>
  constexpr function_ref(constant_wrapper<c, F> f, @\cv{}@ T* obj) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:constraints]
[:en] [`[*is-invocable-using]<const F&, [=cv] T*>] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] [`[*is-invocable-using]<const F&, [=cv] T*>] 为 [`true]。

[para:mandates]
[:en] If [`is_pointer_v<F> || is_member_pointer_v<F>] is [`true],
then [`f.value != nullptr] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`is_pointer_v<F> || is_member_pointer_v<F>] 为 [`true]，则
[`f.value != nullptr] 为 [`true]。

[para:expects]
[:en] If [`is_member_pointer_v<F>] is [`true], [`obj] is not a null pointer.
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`is_member_pointer_v<F>] 为 [`true]，则 [`obj] 不是空指针。

[para:effects]
[:en] Initializes [*bound-entity] with [`obj], and [*thunk-ptr] with the address
of a function [`[^thunk]] such that [`[^thunk]([*bound-entity], [^call-args]...)]
is expression-equivalent ([#defns.expression.equivalent]) to
[`invoke_r<R>(f.value, obj, [^call-args]...)].
[:zh_CN] 以 [`obj] 初始化 [*bound-entity]，并以某个函数 [`[^thunk]] 的地址初始化
[*thunk-ptr]，使得 [`[^thunk]([*bound-entity], [^call-args]...)] 按表达式等价于
（[#defns.expression.equivalent]）[`invoke_r<R>(f.value, obj, [^call-args]...)]。
[div:end]

[%@lib@member operator=[!function_ref]]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<class T> function_ref& operator=(T) = delete;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:constraints]
[list]
[item]
[:en] [`[*is-convertible-from-specialization]<T>] is [`false],
[:zh_CN] [`[*is-convertible-from-specialization]<T>] 为 [`false]，
[item]
[:en] [`is_pointer_v<T>] is [`false], and
[:zh_CN] [`is_pointer_v<T>] 为 [`false]，并且
[item]
[:en] [`T] is not a specialization of [`constant_wrapper].
[:zh_CN] [`T] 不是 [`constant_wrapper] 的特例。
[list:end]
[div:end]
